Thank you so much for this one Zzimba!!! On their "The very best of" "Alcatraz" isn't included (What a disgrace!) but it sure is on this one! :) And you made it in 256 kbps which is really nice.

By the way; 73 downloads and not ONE single thanks or comment... I can't help feeling that many here at TPB are spoiled. Such a great share and not a word in response! Maybe it's a Swedish phenomenon? "I should have everythig for free and not have to give something back"... 

Anyway; thanks again!
Yeah, very nice indeed to deliver some good old naz! Have a hd-crasch so itÂ´s great that I can downloaded it again.

A very good example of the Naz at their best. One of my early favourites, still like it after about 35 years. Thanks so much for helping me through a -30 saturday!
